Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: One Pacific Plaza is a premier Class A office project located in Huntington Beach, California, one of Orange County’s premier oceanfront submarkets. The recently renovated office campus is set apart by it’s industry leading design and construction quality, state-of-the-art building systems, and beautifully landscaped common areas. The property offers convenient freeway access, outdoor seating, ample parking for both tenants and visitors and direct access to unmatched nearby amenities.
